    intro: "Your backyard should be more than grass and a grill on the patio. New England Pavers & Stone designs and builds complete outdoor living environments — kitchens, bars, seating walls, fire features, and entertainment areas — for homeowners across Wakefield and Greater Boston who want to maximize their outdoor season. A well-designed outdoor living space extends your usable home from April through November in New England. Combine your outdoor space with a fire pit installation to push that season even further.",
