    intro: "Steps connect your home to your landscape — and they are often the first thing visitors see. New England Pavers & Stone builds custom stone, granite, and paver steps and staircases for homeowners across Wakefield and Greater Boston. Every stairway we construct meets or exceeds Massachusetts building code requirements for rise, run, landing dimensions, and handrail provisions. Pair new steps with a front walkway replacement for a complete entry transformation.",
